---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="relative w-full overflow-hidden bg-linear-to-b from-black to-[#030715]">
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-7xl flex-col gap-8 px-6 py-12 md:py-14">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-12 md:items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <a href="#home" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white text-xs font-black italic text-black">PF</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-black tracking-[0.16em] text-white">PIXELFLOW STUDIO</span>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#94a3b8]">
          Construim produse digitale rapide, curate si scalabile, cu focus pe conversii si experienta utilizatorului.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-zinc-500">Navigare</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm">
          <a href="/#home" class="text-zinc-300 transition-colors hover:text-white">Acasă</a>
          <a href="/#services" class="text-zinc-300 transition-colors hover:text-white">Servicii</a>
          <a href="/#work" class="text-zinc-300 transition-colors hover:text-white">Proiecte</a>
          <a href="/#testimonials" class="text-zinc-300 transition-colors hover:text-white">Testimoniale</a>
          <a href="/#contact" class="text-zinc-300 transition-colors hover:text-white">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-zinc-500">Date Firma</p>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-300">
          <p>Pixelflow Studio SRL</p>
          <p>CUI RO48765432</p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@pixelflow.studio" class="block transition-colors hover:text-white">hello@pixelflow.studio</a>
          <a href="tel:+40741234567" class="block transition-colors hover:text-white">+40 741 234 567</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 md:grid-cols-12 md:items-center">
      <div class="md:col-span-6">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-zinc-500">Conformitate Consumatori</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
          Afișare pictograme ANPC conform cerințelor pentru comercianți online (SAL/SOL).
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:items-center md:col-span-6 md:justify-end">
        <a
          href="https://anpc.ro/sal/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/15 hover:border-white/30 transition-colors"
          aria-label="Soluționarea Alternativă a Litigiilor - ANPC"
        >
          <img src="https://anpc.ro/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/SAL-PICTOGRAMA.png" alt="ANPC SAL" class="h-[42px] w-[210px] object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://anpc.ro/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/pictogramaSOL.png"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/15 hover:border-white/30 transition-colors"
          aria-label="Soluționarea Online a Litigiilor"
        >
          <img src="https://anpc.ro/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/pictogramaSOL.png" alt="ANPC SOL" class="h-[42px] w-[210px] object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-xs text-zinc-400">
      <a href="/termeni-si-conditii" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Termeni și Condiții</a>
      <a href="/politica-de-confidentialitate" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Politica de Confidențialitate</a>
      <a href="/politica-de-cookies" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Politica de Cookies</a>
    </div>

    <div class="h-px w-full bg-white/10"></div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <p>© {currentYear} Pixelflow Studio. Toate drepturile rezervate.</p>
      <p>Design si dezvoltare in-house.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
